@startuml
actor Reader
participant Frontend as "Profiles Page"
participant Detail as "Profile Detail Page"
participant Backend as "Profiles API"
participant History as "user_book_reads"

Reader -> Frontend: Open /profiles
Frontend -> Backend: GET /api/v1/profiles
Backend -> History: List known reader summaries
History --> Backend: [{ userId, displayName, booksReadCount }]
Backend --> Frontend: ProfilesResponse
Frontend --> Reader: Render reader summary cards

Reader -> Detail: Open /profiles/reader-22
Detail -> Backend: GET /api/v1/profiles/reader-22
Backend -> History: Resolve latest display name + count for reader-22
History --> Backend: displayName + booksReadCount or none
Backend --> Detail: Profile summary or 404
Detail --> Reader: Render reader detail or not-found state
@enduml
